    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's the thing... there isn't anything to find. i've been pretending so long i think the original person actually died or something. i'm just tired of the effort it takes to keep the mask on. it feels so heavy. like, why even bother if nothing is actually happening inside?",
